{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762168262438","path":null,"data":{"id":2558,"title":"AIA:推出「自選人身意外保險 3」及有關產品動態調整","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1703668819333,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;AIA會於<strong><span style=\"color: #fb0909;\">2024年1月15日</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">(首個申請日期)</span> 推出<span style=\"color: #fb0909;\">「自選人身意外保險 3」</span>附加契約，而現行的<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>「自選人身意外保險 2」附加契約將會<span style=\"color: #fb0909; text-decoration: underline;\">停止銷售</span></strong></span>，最後的投保申請日期為<strong><span style=\"color: #fb0909;\">2024年1月14日</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 1.主要<span style=\"color: #f541bc;\">優化</span>了以下項目：</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-12-27/blobid2_ccdae0ef0eda464a8f187d3b5ce61c1d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-12-27/blobid3_1b09e4ded19a4da687e16af36a7f5f55.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 2.「自選人身意外保險 2 - 意外醫療費用賠償」保費調整</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>「自選人身意外保險 2 - 意外醫療費用賠償」</strong></span>的<span style=\"color: #f541bc;\">保費</span>將於<strong><span style=\"color: #fb0909;\">2024年2月24日或以後</span></strong>之保單週年日起作出調整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>3.停止銷售指定個人意外產品</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;AIA會定期檢視現有個人意外產品，並將會<strong><span style=\"color: #fb0909;\">停止銷售</span><span style=\"color: #f541bc;\">「自選人身意外保險 2」及「全意保」綜合意外保險附加契約</span></strong>。已簽署的投保申請書正本須於<strong><span style=\"color: #fb0909;\">2024年1月14日或之前遞交</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-12-27/blobid0_aeb809dceac6442fbebac8420fa5115b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"自選人身意外保險3_showdoc_TC.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-12-27/自選人身意外保險3_showdoc_TC_8876273ddb72429f99fe77e2e9b94826.pdf","uploadTime":1703661281450,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"PAC_Select_3.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-12-27/PAC_Select_3_601db088a22a4b84963585bdf4af5ddb.pdf","uploadTime":1703661281450,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"A2023255.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-12-27/A2023255_eba9a14bfb7e41fbaa44bbdbcd75fbd1.pdf","uploadTime":1703661281455,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"AIA","companyName":"友邦保險","productCodes":["AIA:PS2AMERB","AIA:AIR","AIA:PS3ADDB","AIA:PS